OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's announcement of a
OL,7,F#22 billion investment in Merseyside
OL,8,Fand Teesside for Carbon Capture
OL,9,Ftechnology has been widely welcomed as
OL,10,Fa step in the right direction on
OL,11,Ftackling climate change.
OL,13,FBut what does it actually mean?
OL,15,FCarbon capture isn't a new idea - it
OL,16,Fwas first trialled in America as long
OL,17,Fago as 1972.
OL,19,FBut with climate change gathering pace
OL,20,Frapidly there's a new urgency to
OL,21,Ffinding methods of dealing with it.
