OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FCarbon dioxide, or CO2, is a major
OL,7,Fdriver of climate change.
OL,9,FA naturally occurring gas, modern
OL,10,Findustrial processes and fossil fuels
OL,11,Fhave helped produce an overload in the
OL,12,Fatmosphere which is adding to global
OL,13,Fwarming and climate change.
OL,15,FIn simple terms Carbon Capture and
OL,16,FStorage (CCS) does what it says on the
OL,17,Ftin.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
