OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FIn a three stage process excess CO2
OL,7,Fproduced by power generation or
OL,8,Findustrial processes such as steel
OL,9,Fmaking is separated at source from
OL,10,Fother gases.
OL,12,FIt is then transported by pipeline,
OL,13,Froad or in ships to a storage facility.
OL,15,FThe third and final element of the
OL,16,Fprocess is the storage of the gas
OL,17,Funderground, in the case of the North
OL,18,FWest development deep under Liverpool
OL,19,FBay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
