OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FIn a related process Carbon Capture,
OL,7,FUtilisation and Storage (CCUS) the
OL,8,Fcaptured CO2 is reused in industrial
OL,9,Fprocesses, producing for example
OL,10,Fbiofuel, plastics or concrete.
OL,12,FThis all sounds great - but is it safe?
OL,14,FSupporters of this approach point out
OL,15,Fthat it involves proven technology
OL,16,Fthat has operated safely for 45 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
