OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FThis system aims to prevent too much
OL,7,FCO2 from getting into the atmosphere
OL,8,Faltogether, working along with
OL,9,Fmeasures to remove the excess already
OL,10,Fthere, such as restoring peat bogs or
OL,11,Fplanting more trees which are natural
OL,12,FCO2 traps.
OL,14,FEmma Pinchbeck, Chief Executive of
OL,15,FEnergy UK, described CCUS as a "tool
OL,16,Fin our armoury of technologies which
OL,17,Fwe need to decarbonise parts of energy
OL,18,Fthat we currently can't do with clean
OL,19,Felectricity, such as major industrial
OL,20,Fprocesses".
