OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FJames Richardson, acting Chief
OL,7,FExecutive of the Climate Change
OL,8,FCommittee, said: "It's fantastic to
OL,9,Fsee funding coming through for these
OL,10,Fbig projects.
OL,12,F"We can't hit the country's targets
OL,13,Fwithout CCUS so this commitment to it
OL,14,Fis very reassuring."
OL,16,FBut Greenpeace UK's Policy Director,
OL,17,FDoug Parr, said #22 billion "is a lot
OL,18,Fof money to spend on something that is
OL,19,Fgoing to extend the life of planet-
OL,20,Fheating oil and gas production".
