OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FWhile he acknowledged it was vital the
OL,7,FGovernment committed to industrial
OL,8,Finvestment and job creation while
OL,9,Ftackling the climate crisis, "it needs
OL,10,Fto be the right sort of industries".
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News' Rob Smith, the
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,14,Fdefended plans to invest in carbon
OL,15,Fcapture technology in Merseyside.
