OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister claims this
OL,7,Ftechnology would create thousands of
OL,8,Fjobs for workers in the North West,
OL,9,Fwhile also allowing polluting
OL,10,Findustries to survive as the UK
OL,11,Fapproaches their net zero goals.
OL,13,FHe said: "We are transitioning to
OL,14,Frenewable energy because it's cheaper,
OL,15,Fwe get independence, and we get many
OL,16,Fjobs with it, but we also have to
OL,17,Frecognise that when it comes to
OL,18,Fsectors like glass or cement it's
OL,19,Fvirtually impossible to manufacture
OL,20,Fwithout some carbon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
