OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,F"What this does is it allows us to
OL,7,Fcapture that carbon... put it back in
OL,8,Fthe ground and put it back in the
OL,9,Fground essentially where it came from."
OL,11,FBut Cllr Tom Crone, the leader of the
OL,12,FGreen Group on Liverpool Council,
OL,13,Fargues it is a "costly distraction"
OL,14,Fand urged the government to invest in
OL,15,F"true green fuels".
