OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FHe said: "It's completely unproven at
OL,7,Fany kind of scale and likely to
OL,8,Fgenerate energy at a much higher cost
OL,9,Fthan renewable and other forms of
OL,10,Fenergy, I really believe it's only
OL,11,Fgoing to benefit the fossil fuel
OL,12,Fcompanies so they can carry on
OL,13,Fextracting fossil fuels.
OL,15,F"They really should instead be
OL,16,Finvesting in home insulation to save
OL,17,Fpeople money off their bills and
OL,18,Fincreasing investment in renewables
OL,19,Ffor clean energy that we really need
OL,20,Ffor the future."
