OL,3,CWhat is Carbon Capture and will it
OL,4,Chelp save the environment?
OL,6,FCllr Tom Crone, of the Green Party,
OL,7,Fset out the pitfalls he believes there
OL,8,Fare with Carbon Capture
OL,10,FThe government sees CCS as a means of
OL,11,Freaching its legally binding net zero
OL,12,Fcommitment by 2050, essentially
OL,13,Fbalancing the amount of climate change
OL,14,Fgreenhouse gases we produce with the
OL,15,Famount we remove.
OL,17,FIt is a growing technology and
OL,18,Findustry experts say that by 2022
OL,19,Fthere were 194 large scale facilities
OL,20,Facross the world with 73 of those in
OL,21,FEurope.
